len Beitrag die Audioführung im Zusammenspiel mit anderen Begleitmedien zu leisten in der Lage ist.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 3.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/3.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aAusstellungen. 4aKulturelle Bildung. 4aKunst. 4aMuseum. 4aPädagogen. 7aART / Museum Studies.2bisacsh  aArts.  aCultural Education.  aMuseum.40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839402269zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de GruyterzOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839402269zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839402269/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-GOA